++ Note: This is a Black Highlighter based theme. You will need to import the Black Highlighter theme as well in order to use this theme. [http://www.scp-wiki.net/theme:black-highlighter-theme To learn more go here.]

+++ Additionally, this is a heavily modified variant of the incredible [[[component: Old Money theme] by [[*user djkaktus]] & [[*user woedenaz]]

